parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The defective Takata airbag inflator can cause the airbag to deploy inadvertently or rupture, leading to serious injury or fatality.
symptoms: Abnormal sounds from the airbag system
concern about potential airbag deployment.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The cracked rear lift gate housing can compromise the integrity of the rear door, allowing it to open from the inside and outside, which can lead to accidents, injuries, and potential security risks.
symptoms: The rear latch is not fully operational
the rear door opens unexpectedly
the rear door does not close properly
the rear door glass window portion is compromised.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Automatic Rear Lift Gate Closure Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the automatic rear lift gate closure system can cause injuries, such as lacerations and concussions, as the gate continues to close despite sensing obstacles.
symptoms: The rear lift gate continues to close despite sensing obstacles
the rear lift gate does not retract when sensing an object
the rear lift gate closes unexpectedly
the rear lift gate does not respond to the automatic closure feature.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Brake Booster and Master Cylinder Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake booster and master cylinder can cause a loss of braking power, leading to increased stopping distances, accidents, and potentially serious injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: Very light brake pedal
brake pedal goes all the way to the floor before the vehicle starts to slow down
brake and VDC lights come on
brakes skip and truck slides
vehicle rolls away on its own when parked.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Electrical Fire Originating from the Steering Column
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: An electrical fire originating from the steering column can cause significant damage to the vehicle, potentially leading to injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: Explosion or loud noise
smoke coming from the vehicle
flames under the steering column
console
and accelerator pedal.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of power window motors can cause inconvenience and discomfort to the driver and passengers, and may lead to further electrical issues if not addressed.
symptoms: Power windows malfunctioning or failing to operate
windows getting stuck or falling down
repeated failures of power window motors.
